fields.name: BXF GIRLIE COOL CONTRAST ZOODIE
fields.product_description: Ideal for throwing on to and from the gym on those chilly nights, this cool sports zoodie combines wicking performance with lightly brushed fabric making it soft on the body. The adjustable attached hood featuring drawcords protects from the elements while the raglan sleeves and thumb holes offer great range of motion. Features the BXF logo left breast, right cuff and on the bottom of back.

fields.name: ADIDAS TECH FALL 2.0 BOOTS
fields.product_description: Combining Adidas's top tooling with a mesh upper that has been reinforced from the inside these Tech Fall 2.0 boots from Adidas are a must to have. They have all the features you have come to expect flexibility, breathability, grip and support, these boots are blended on a high level. The knitted mesh uppers provide breathability, lightweight and strong support in all areas.

fields.name: CLETO REYES SPARRING HEADGUARD
fields.product_description: Cleto Reyes boxing equipment of Mexico is like no other boxing equipment supplier. Cleto Reyes Headguard is manufactured from leather. This boxing headguard has cheek protection with a lace tie on top and two hook and loop rear straps and a chin strap fastening for a superior fit.

fields.name: ADIDAS KIDS BOXING GLOVES AND FOCUS MITTS SET
fields.product_description: This boxing set is ideal for beginner pad sessions to get the bug for boxing. The set includes 1 pair of boxing gloves and 1 pair of focus mitts so everything you need to get going

fields.name: BXF MOVER JOGGERS
fields.product_description: Understated and comfortable these BXF jogger pants is cut in premium 300gsm 85% organic cotton, 15% recycled polyester brushed fabric. With adjustable drawcord on the waistband, a patch pocket on the back and the BXF printed logo left leg, you’re covered on your training day to your rest day.

fields.name: BYTOMIC RUBBER MEDICINE BALL - 5KG
fields.product_description: Medicine balls are great for a complete body workout, wether your in the gym or at home. The Bytomic Rubber Medicine Ball can be used to strengthen shoulders, back and arms as well as improving core strength with a wide range of exercises. Made from rubber material makes them easy grip as well as a waterproof and easy to clean. Available in a range of weights, so you can pick the perfect weight for all your strength training needs.

fields.name: ADIDAS BOXING TARGET PADDLES
fields.product_description: Mix up the workout and use these Adidas Boxing Target Paddles that make a great alternative or supplement to punch mitts. With their easier to grip handle they also feature a wrist loop for security. Covered in a PU vinyl cover with a dense foam filling so they can handle the punishment you give them!

fields.name: Pro Fitness Weighted Skipping Rope
fields.product_description: Add something a little bit extra to your skipping exericse with this weighted skipping rope. Perfect for fitness exercises, speed training, boxing, and crossfit, whether you're at the gym or at home. It's ideal for people looking to tone muscle, lose weight and build their cardio endurance. The length of the skipping rope can be adjusted to suit you as the weight of the jump rope adds an extra element to your cardio training.

fields.name: Pro Fitness Speed Rope
fields.product_description: Perfect for building your cardio endurance, stamina and speed, this Pro Fitness Speed Rope will have you skipping around at home or the gym like a pro. The 300mm cable's length is fully adjustable by using its large screws, making it ideal for any person's height. The wire cable means no kinking, tangling or bending like the usual PVC and leather ropes so you can focus on training.

fields.name: Genuine Thermos Hydration Aubergine Bottle - 710ml
fields.product_description: With our Thermos hydration bottles, staying hydrated has never been easier! Always BPA-free, these bottles are perfectly designed to help keep you on your feet no matter what. The measuring levels on the side of the bottle let you monitor your daily consumption easily and effectively. This bottle is perfect for a life on the move as the lid uses a one-handed, push-button mechanism so you don't have to stop to drink. Including an integrated carry-loop for easy transportation, you'll never leave this bottle behind!

fields.name: Everlast Hand Wraps - 274cm
fields.product_description: These hand wraps from Everlast are designed to provide extra protection and support you while you practice your best boxing or martial arts moves. They feature breathable thumb straps for full mobility and offer comfort as you train. These high quality hand wraps come with easy to follow instructions for first time users.

fields.name: Adidas 450cm Hand Wraps
fields.product_description: These hand wraps are ideal for not only boxing but all combat sports. Not only will they aid in both hand and wrist protection while training or during sparring sessions, the non-abrasive stretch material will help to keep you comfortable throughout.

fields.name: OPRO POWER-FIT BRACES
fields.product_description: Having braces should not mean you sacrifice the retention or comfort of your mouthguard. That’s why these Opro Power-Fit gum shields are ideal for braces wearers too. The difference between these and our Opro's original Power-Fit gumshields is these allow the space to accommodate for your braces. You still get a custom-fit, professional retention, and a full range of styles and colours.

fields.name: PhD 1.5L Water Bottle 1.5L
fields.product_description: The PhD water bottle comes in an eye-catching smoked black colour. Strong and durable it comes with a leak-proof stainless steel screw top lid and red strap which attaches to the bottle to help avoid losses, making it the perfect product for your desk or gym bag.

fields.name: Opti 10kg Weighted Vest
fields.product_description: Perfect for adding an extra element to your strength and cross fit training, this weighted vest will help you increase the intensity and efficiency of your workout. The front and back weights are evenly distributed to support your optimum performance, and you can easily remove the weights to adjust your resistance level. One size fits most and the waist is Velcro to give you safety and protection while you use it.

fields.name: Thermos Guardian 710ml Hydration Bottle
fields.product_description: New to the Thermos range, The Guardian Series is stylish yet understated, designed with unique technology enhancements. Available in 2 colourways, our 710ml hydration bottle is perfect for the daily commute or people on the go. Created with the Thermos quality and performance you can rely on and with a 5-year guarantee, this hydration bottle is a style icon.

fields.name: Pro Fitness 10kg Weighted Vest
fields.product_description: Add intensity to any workout with the Pro Fitness weighted vest. With a tapered design and adjustable side straps for a close fit, this vest will keep you looking cool while you work up a sweat. Great for any type of exercise from pull ups and push ups, to cardio training on a treadmill or stepper. With removable weights, this vest is suitable for a variety of fitness levels, and will keep you challenged as your strength and fitness improve.

fields.name: Opti Deluxe Skipping Rope
fields.product_description: Increase your agility and balance with this 9ft Skipping Rope. The foam covered handles provide extra comfort, while the ball bearings offer speed and smoothness of rotation.

fields.name: TUF WEAR HEAVY DUTY BARREL SLIP BAG WITH CHAIN
fields.product_description: This Tuf Wear Heavy Duty PU Barrel Slip bag is a great alternative to any traditional style slip bag. A slip bag can help you perfect your footwork and take it to new levels whilst improving your reactions. Comes complete with a chain for easy hanging.

fields.name: PRO BOX ORIGINAL MAIZE BAG
fields.product_description: The Pro Box Original Leather Maize Bag is a heavy duty soft leather maize bag and comes from Pro Box's original range that brings together the best in proven design and modern technology. This maize bag is suitable for intense use uppercut training and is filled with plastic granules.

fields.name: ADIDAS GOLD PRINT BOXING HOODY
fields.product_description: Perfect for throwing on after a workout or on those well earned non-training days. Comfortable and warm, all you'd expect from Adidas.

fields.name: ADIDAS HYBRID 150 FOCUS MITTS
fields.product_description: Practise your offensive and defensive movements with these Adidas Hybrid 150 Focus Mitts. Constructed from PU with a thick foam padding that provides optimal shock absorption. They feature a padded palm that includes a grip ball. These pads will help evoke the ebb and flow of a real fight.

fields.name: ADIDAS ADISTAR PRO GROIN GUARD METALLIC
fields.product_description: This Adidas top of the range premium Groin Guard has been designed with comfort and protection in mind and a great look. It features various layers of foam to absorb shock and impact to protect the most sensitive area. The moulded shape ensures you get an optimal fit while the lace system provides a secure and firm closure.

fields.name: ADIDAS ADISPEED 501 BOXING GLOVES - LIMITED EDITION
fields.product_description: Check out the limited edition colourways in these Adidas Adispeed Boxing Gloves. Designed in the USA they are crafted from high-quality genuine leather with one piece injection mould for ideal shock absorption and impact protection. For supreme comfort, they feature a soft inner lining and the rigid strap provides a firm and secure closure.

fields.name: ADIDAS ADISPEED 501 HOOK & LOOP BOXING GLOVES METALLIC
fields.product_description: Bring on your shine with these premium top of the range lace up boxing gloves from Adidas. Crafted from high-quality genuine leather that feature various layers of foam that is ideal shock absorption and impact protection. For supreme comfort, they feature a soft inner lining and the rigid strap ensures a secure fit.

fields.name: ADIDAS LEATHER PRO SPEED 550 FOCUS MITTS
fields.product_description: Help improve your form, focus and accuracy with these Adidas Leather Pro Speed 550 focus mitts. The leather perforated fingers help to keep you cool whilst the multi-layered padding gives you ultimate shock absorption. For a secure fit they also feature an adjustable wrist strap.

fields.name: ADIDAS THAI BOXING SHORTS
fields.product_description: These Adidas Thai Boxing Shorts have an authentic Muay Thai cut with Thai prints on both sides. They are lightweight to make them really comfortable whilst fighting. The large elasticated waistband with a cord tightening has a contrast 3 stripes design and the Adidas logo on the waistband.

fields.name: BOXFIT ANTHEM HOODIE
fields.product_description: You won't want to take this great hoodie off. The Boxfit men's Anthem hoodie is a luxuriously thick and boasts a soft-feel finish inside and out for extreme comfort. Every detail on this hoodie has been meticulously thought out to create a high impact top. Great for throwing on for training or for those chill out rest days.

fields.name: Adidas Hybrid 100 16oz Boxing Gloves - Black
fields.product_description: An outstanding multi-purpose glove that is excellent for pad work, bag work, sparring and fitness training. This really is the ultimate all-rounder. With inside lining for comfort, two piece injection mould foam padding and two-tone rigid elasticated strap that can be secured solidly to provide extra support. Designed with an ergonomic shape for a powerful and fast punch.

fields.name: BOXFIT TECHNICAL POLO SHIRT
fields.product_description: This Boxfit UK Technical Polo Shirt is produced using high quality material and advanced manufacturing methods which is designed to endure the rigours of regular wear and washing. Careful attention has been taken in the garment design, fit and functionality and this polo shirt has an active fit. It is light weight and made from polyester micro pinhole material and flat lock seam with silver coverstitch. Its quick dry and easy care as well.
